    ISourceLocation, IASNode, IBinaryOperatorNode, IExpressionNode, IIdentifierNode, IMemberAccessExpressionNode, IOperatorNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    QualifiedNamespaceExpressionNode

    public class FullNameNode
extends MemberAccessExpressionNode
implements IIdentifierNode
    Node for a fully qualified name (e.g. mx.core.Button) used in a package or class definition. This is really just a MemberAccessExpressionNode where all of the pieces are guaranteed to be simple IdentifierNodes.
